<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<title>Marker HIRO — Champagne & Territoire</title>
<style>
  @page { size:A4; margin:12mm; }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body {
    font-family:Georgia,serif; background:white;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;
    justify-content:center; min-height:100vh;
    gap:7mm; padding:10mm; text-align:center;
  }
  h1   { font-size:17pt; color:#1a3a08; letter-spacing:.06em; }
  .sub { font-size:9pt; color:#666; }
  .wrap {
    border:8mm solid black; padding:6mm; background:white;
    display:inline-block; image-rendering:pixelated;
  }
  .wrap img { display:block; width:120mm; height:120mm; image-rendering:pixelated; }
  .badge {
    background:#1a3a08; color:white; font-size:7.5pt;
    letter-spacing:.2em; padding:2mm 7mm; text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .prods { display:flex; gap:4mm; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .prod  { border:1px solid #c9a84c; padding:1.5mm 5mm; font-size:8pt; color:#8b6914; }
  .info  {
    font-size:8.5pt; color:#444; line-height:1.9;
    border-top:1px solid #ccc; padding-top:5mm; max-width:145mm;
  }
  .info b { color:#1a3a08; display:block; margin-bottom:1mm; }
  @media print { .noprint { display:none; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Champagne &amp; Territoire — AR</h1>
<div class="sub">Marker universale · Funziona per tutti e 3 i prodotti</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Marker Hiro AR.js"/>
</div>

<div class="badge">MARKER HIRO — AR.js preset</div>

<div class="prods">
  <div class="prod">🍾 Champagne AOC</div>
  <div class="prod">🌾 Blé de Champagne</div>
  <div class="prod">🧀 Chaource AOP</div>
</div>

<div class="info">
  <b>Come usare:</b>
  1. Stampa in bianco e nero su carta A4 — non plastificare<br>
  2. Apri la Camera AR e scegli il prodotto con i pulsanti<br>
  3. Tieni il foglio fermo su piano orizzontale<br>
  4. Distanza fotocamera: 20–40 cm · buona illuminazione
</div>

<button class="noprint" onclick="window.print()"
  style="padding:8px 24px;background:#1a3a08;color:white;border:none;
         font-size:10pt;cursor:pointer;font-family:Georgia,serif;margin-top:3mm">
  🖨 Stampa
</button>

</body>
</html>

